message.text: I'm great as well. I love the picture of your dog! :)
His name is Wilson. The weather seems to be great next weekend. Would you like to go for a dog park date?
Hi, I'm doing great. And you?
Thank you! His name is George. :) What's the name of your dog?
Love the name! And yes, I saw that too. I was planning on going to the new park in Bothel, let's meet there at noon! :)
Clever! Do you believe in love at first sight, or do I have to swim past you again?
Of course! ;) Who doesn't?! Wanna go out for a sushi date? haha.
Haha I promise not to say anything. How's Thursday at 730pm sound?
Whats a beautiful gull like you doing in a rubbish dump like this?
Hahaha :D, that's pretty good. I guess you love cheesy pickup lines to?
Wow, I'd be a terrible fish own if I said yes haha. But yes, we just can't let my fish Jasper know. He might have a problem with that! Haha
